What's up with the name Fan? [#name]
====================================
"The Fan" is the [neighborhood]`http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fan_district`
where we live in Richmond, VA.  It's a great turn of the 20th century
neighborhood back when urban planning was human-centric as opposed
to automobile-centric.  It also has the added bonus of being a very
short word!

How is Fan licensed? [#license]
