What is the status of Fan? [#status]
====================================
Fan is currently in [development]`Roadmap#status`.

How do Fan version numbers work? [#versions]
============================================
Fan version numbers are a three or four part series of decimal
integers separated by dots: 'major.minor.build.patch'.  We are
currently developing version 1.0 as a series of incrementing
builds: 1.0.30, 1.0.31, etc.


